<s-1 id="RM00000282Q000X_01_0012" proc-id="RM0250U___0000BQW00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL ATF TEMPERATURE SENSOR ASSEMBLY</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Coat a new O-ring with ATF and install it to the ATF temperature sensor assembly.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C138520E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Coat the 4 bolts with ATF.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C138522" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the ATF temperature sensor assembly and clamp to the valve body assembly with the 4 bolts.</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>11</t-value1>
<t-value2>112</t-value2>
<t-value4>8</t-value4>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM00000282Q000X_01_0013" proc-id="RM0250U___0000BQX00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL TRANSMISSION WIRE</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Connect the 8 connectors to the valve body assembly.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C138519" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Coat the O-ring with ATF.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C142570E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Coat the bolt with ATF.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C138518" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the transmission wire and lock plate to the valve body assembly with the bolt.</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>11</t-value1>
<t-value2>112</t-value2>
<t-value4>8</t-value4>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
</content1>
